## Complete File Structure

```
voice-coding-assistant/
├── .env                          # API keys (OpenRouter)
├── .eslintrc.json                # ESLint configuration
├── .gitignore                    # Git ignore rules
├── .vscode/
│   ├── launch.json               # F5 debug configuration
│   └── tasks.json                # Build task
├── package.json                  # Extension manifest
├── tsconfig.json                 # TypeScript config
├── requirements.txt              # Python dependencies
├── src/
│   ├── extension.ts              # Main entry point (952 lines)
│   ├── voiceRecorder.ts          # Microphone recording via SoX
│   ├── speechToText.ts           # Hybrid STT sidecar client
│   ├── stt_service.py            # Python sidecar (Vosk+Whisper+VAD)
│   ├── commandParser.ts          # Voice → structured command (983 lines)
│   ├── commandDictionary.ts      # 120+ command reference (1078 lines)
│   ├── aiEngine.ts               # OpenRouter AI code generation
│   ├── syntaxDetector.ts         # Language detection (942 lines)
│   ├── vscodeController.ts       # VS Code API actions (705 lines)
│   ├── wakeWordDetector.ts       # Wake/deactivation phrase matching
│   ├── voiceFeedback.ts          # Text-to-speech responses
│   └── voiceModeManager.ts       # Passive/Active state machine
├── out/                          # Compiled JavaScript output
├── node_modules/                 # Node.js dependencies
└── .venv/                        # Python virtual environment
```

