## Voice Activation System

### Wake Phrases (Activate)

| Phrase | Notes |
|--------|-------|
| **"Hey Coder"** | Primary wake phrase |
| "Start voice coding" | Alternative |
| "Activate coding assistant" | Alternative |
| "Start coding" | Short form |
| "Wake up" | Short form |
| "Activate assistant" | Alternative |

### Indian Accent Variations (Auto-detected)

| What You Say | Whisper May Hear | Result |
|-------------|-----------------|--------|
| "Hey Coder" | "hey coda" | ✅ Activated |
| "Hey Coder" | "hey koder" | ✅ Activated |
| "Hey Coder" | "a coder" | ✅ Activated |
| "Hey Coder" | "hay coder" | ✅ Activated |

### Deactivation Phrases

| Phrase | Notes |
|--------|-------|
| **"Stop voice coding"** | Primary |
| "Deactivate assistant" | Alternative |
| "Sleep assistant" | Alternative |
| "Go to sleep" | Alternative |
| "Goodbye" | Alternative |
| "Stop listening" | Alternative |

### How It Works

```
User speaks → SoX records 3s clip → Vosk (fast check)
                                         │
                          ┌───────────────┴───────────────┐
                          │ Potential wake word?           │
                          │ (contains "hey", "coder", etc)│
                          └───────────┬───────────────────┘
                                      │
                               ┌──────┴──────┐
                               │             │
                            No│           Yes│
                               │             │
                     Continue  │    Whisper   │
                     passive   │    verifies  │
                     listening │             │
                               │    ┌────────┴────────┐
                               │    │ Wake confirmed? │
                               │    └────────┬────────┘
                               │          Yes│
                               │    ┌────────┴────────┐
                               │    │ ACTIVATE!       │
                               │    │ Switch to       │
                               │    │ ACTIVE mode     │
                               │    └─────────────────┘
```

