## Real-Time Performance

### Latency Breakdown

| Stage | Duration | Notes |
|-------|----------|-------|
| SoX Recording | 3s (passive) / 7s (active) | Configurable |
| Silero VAD | ~50ms | Instant silence detection |
| Vosk Streaming | ~100ms | Wake-word detection |
| Whisper Small | ~500ms | Accurate transcription |
| Command Parsing | <10ms | Regex matching |
| VS Code Action | <50ms | API call |
| **Total** | **<1s after recording** | Well under 2s target |

### Optimization Techniques

1. **Persistent sidecar**: Models loaded once, kept in memory
2. **Silero VAD**: Skips processing for silent clips
3. **Passive/Active modes**: Vosk-fast for wake words, Whisper for accuracy
4. **Chunked audio processing**: Vosk processes in streaming chunks
5. **JSON line protocol**: Minimal IPC overhead

