## Voice Feedback System

The assistant speaks confirmations using the OS text-to-speech engine:

| Action | Spoken Feedback |
|--------|----------------|
| File created | "File calculator.py created" |
| File saved | "File saved" |
| Navigation | "Moved to line 10" |
| Code generated | "Function inserted" |
| Activation | "Voice coding assistant activated" |
| Deactivation | "Voice assistant deactivated" |
| Error | "An error occurred" |
| No speech | "Could not detect speech" |
| Program run | "Running file" |

### Platform Support

| OS | TTS Engine | Command |
|----|-----------|---------|
| Windows | System.Speech | `PowerShell SpeechSynthesizer` |
| macOS | Built-in say | `say -r 200 "message"` |
| Linux | espeak / spd-say | `espeak "message"` |

